<section class="home-challenges">
  <div class="home-challenges-inner">
    <h2 class="home-challenges-heading">Why Generation AI?</h2>
    <p class="home-challenges-lead">The project was launched in response to three interconnected societal challenges.</p>
    <div class="home-challenges-grid">

      <div class="home-challenge-card">
        <div class="home-challenge-num">01</div>
        <h3 class="home-challenge-title">A weaker sense of safety and control</h3>
        <p class="home-challenge-text">Datafication and AI systems can undermine people’s sense that they control their own lives and decisions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="home-challenge-card">
        <div class="home-challenge-num">02</div>
        <h3 class="home-challenge-title">Erosion of trust</h3>
        <p class="home-challenge-text">Algorithmic environments can weaken trust in authorities, science, media, and civil society.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="home-challenge-card">
        <div class="home-challenge-num">03</div>
        <h3 class="home-challenge-title">Growing digital inequality</h3>
        <p class="home-challenge-text">Rapid technological change deepens skills gaps: those with digital agency move forward, others are left behind.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

